body_html:
@shashishekhar
I attach original graph and frozen graph using freeze_graph script
graph.tar.gz

  1. freeze graph
    bazel build tensorflow/python/tools:freeze_graph &&
    bazel-bin/tensorflow/python/tools/freeze_graph
    --input_graph=/root/DNNSE/model/graph.pb
    --input_checkpoint=/root/DNNSE/model/epoch_71.ckpt-71
    --output_graph=/root/DNNSE/model/frozen_graph.pb
    --output_node_names=Mean

  2. toco
    bazel build tensorflow/contrib/lite/toco:toco &&
    toco --graph_def_file=/root/DNNSE/model/frozen_graph.pb
    --input_format=TENSORFLOW_GRAPHDEF
    --output_format=TFLITE
    --output_file=/root/DNNSE/model/tflite_model.lite
    --inference_type=FLOAT
    --input_type=FLOAT
    --input_arrays=x
    --output_arrays=Mean
    --input_shapes=64,257

body:
@shashishekhar 
I attach original graph and frozen graph using freeze_graph script
[graph.tar.gz](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/files/2217777/graph.tar.gz)

1. freeze graph
bazel build tensorflow/python/tools:freeze_graph && \
bazel-bin/tensorflow/python/tools/freeze_graph \
--input_graph=/root/DNNSE/model/graph.pb \
--input_checkpoint=/root/DNNSE/model/epoch_71.ckpt-71 \
--output_graph=/root/DNNSE/model/frozen_graph.pb \
--output_node_names=Mean

2. toco
bazel build tensorflow/contrib/lite/toco:toco && \
toco --graph_def_file=/root/DNNSE/model/frozen_graph.pb \
--input_format=TENSORFLOW_GRAPHDEF \
--output_format=TFLITE \
--output_file=/root/DNNSE/model/tflite_model.lite \
--inference_type=FLOAT \
--input_type=FLOAT \
--input_arrays=x \
--output_arrays=Mean \
--input_shapes=64,257
